Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波比  嘘…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}在日本每天早上我都会先叫醒忍再去信箱里收报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}冬天我会穿厚厚的大衣而夏天我会在门前洒洒水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)\fs55.5}之后我会和忍的妈妈还有勇姐打个招呼  然后再去忍的房间看看她起来了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}她总是很贪睡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}波比  还记得忍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)\fs54}R E N  忍  一个在初中的时候来我们家homestay的学生  她看起来就像日本木娃娃一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}我们都叫她忍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.88,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Daily live in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:33.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Eveny morning I check the mail box to pick up the newspapers after I try to wake up Shino.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I wear a Paris short coat when it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I also sow water in front of the door in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I greet Shino's mom and Isami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:48.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,And I go to Shino's room again to wake up if she is still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,She has trouble to getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Popy.Do you remember Shino?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:00.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,SHI NO BU, a japanese middle school student hold her homestay in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:02.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,She looks like a Kokesi Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,We call her Shino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  我好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  我不想在装下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你嘛  可怜  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:03:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到英国以后  爱丽丝你也总是在说忍的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:07.91,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\fs45\pos(1635,652)}Episode11  \N不管怎样  最最…\N最喜欢的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜  你回来之后倒是天天拿着个摄像机在拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我要给大家带去和日本不一样的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice idea  那多拍点建筑物之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nonono  这是「好想见忍  爱丽丝哭哭哦」特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天就去买礼物吧  购物咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天买的东西都堆成山了  够多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能平平安安过去才算是最好的礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  但是等我们过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍她还会记得我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会记得啦  homestay之后3年没见面却都还记得彼此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回不才一个礼拜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是忍她前阵子不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥本哈根是哪个国家的首都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一般的忘记而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那她还是记得我们的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定也很想见我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚是奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  大和抚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  你还记得忍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑你喜欢的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪鹿蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜你太强了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花牌我好久不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和忍也在这间屋子里玩过花牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  要不要给忍打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了  现在日本那边已经是夜晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得爱丽丝和忍不带手机有点不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在看来带着也不是很方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想说的话我写信就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和忍的话一定会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不也是要花很长时间么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  可怜  我现在在做司康饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜登场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多做点心上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨  这样行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  可怜你手法很娴熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在忍那里也做过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在一起开过茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍很来劲但是做东西耗了很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来还是第二天在学校里吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在庭院里摊了张塑料布  感觉有点像野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜做的芝麻小饼也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗乃花和老师们都觉得挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问绫借来心型的模具做了好多心形饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子把面粉弄翻的时候真是一团糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨手笨脚的阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜来之前忍还把橙汁给弄翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨手笨脚的忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多让我听听你们在日本的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热腾腾的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有冰淇淋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}时间过得真快  一个礼拜这就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}爱丽丝  你爸爸明天会送你去机场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Time flys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,One week already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Alice, your dad will give you a ride to the airport tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,That's nice on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}爸爸  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的爸爸妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会在机场等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得家里一起出去玩  结果你都在我家里玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}你们俩看起来都很熟悉日本的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}讲起话来用的都是日语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}不过我还是不敢相信你们居然餐餐都有纳豆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Both of you seem to be getting used to live in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,You guys talk to each other in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:32.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides...I can't believe you eat Natto every meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易才从日本带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要是能和大家一起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过绫看起来好像不太敢坐飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子来的话她不会不跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是地球的另一边还是宇宙的任何一处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等回去日本后暑假都要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二学期很有盼头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运动会和学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有忍纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定得办个派对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我有点等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈欠都传给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你拉我回英国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不快点睡早上就要赖床了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打个电话到日本那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的那天没给她打  今天一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔了一个礼拜的对话  令人心跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鹿乱撞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别说了啦  可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  手抖得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打个电话都这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我选这张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍看来撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝打电话过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地满血复活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算和爱丽丝说上话了  甚好甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  忍看起来也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  她怎么定住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,难道爱丽丝出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}你好吗  忍？ 我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}可怜  妈妈  爸爸还有波比也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝在飚英语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}我马上就要赶飞机了  日本时间九点到你那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.61,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}可怜和我买了好多好多礼物给你们  敬请期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)\fs55.5}我也希望你能喜欢它们  在英国我过的挺快乐的  这里给了我美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}我妈妈和家里人也都很开心  等我回来了我仔细和你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}我  我不知道该说什么好了  这么长时间没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,How are you, Shino?I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Karan, Mom and Popy are also well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the time to catch the flight soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I will be in Japan among the morning 4 time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Karan and I got a lot of gifts for you so look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I hope you'll like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm enjoying being in UK it became memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,My mom and family are happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:13.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,I...I don't know what to say. It's been such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是在对话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.72,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,hello hello
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是咧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  那个  刚才对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  电话给我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  过得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物我们买了好多你就认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝也很过得挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还说在英国勾起了她的思乡之情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要挂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没谈上几句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝你说了好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  忍她一定听懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又没能和爱丽丝好好说上话啊  真够遗憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这次好好谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说了好多英语  我也hello的给她回应了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么东西忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算上这个就齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个  时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意身体啊  爱丽丝就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时欢迎你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等着你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是乎  爱丽丝她们也快要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她会去洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪得一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你出去等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了  忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  你们一路平安真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一个星期真是太漫长了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  毕竟那时没能送你们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那个蝴蝶结是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的动作根本是在说「礼物就是我」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还带了很多礼物给你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己选自己喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是红茶吗  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是格雷伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇也来选礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最后一个选就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大宫忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是「好想见忍  爱丽丝哭哭哦」影像集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝现在非常地消沉  我来扮作忍给她打打气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时差怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我在飞机上睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在爱丽丝不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寂寞地小哭了一会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说说你回英国时的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？忍你暑假的作业一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明明说了会在我回老家的时候做完的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  或许下次你会因为一些别的什么再哭一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上她才写完了暑假作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是踩着线合格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为有爱丽丝在就没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么大能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍  你掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面都是马赛克我什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英语考试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不好好学习  再过半年你就要准备升学了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绫  别这样责怪忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她学习确实很烂  但她有特殊的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她考试分数才5分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜  你的声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊的才能？什么才能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如转盘子  转转转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没转过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的  很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没转就打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't mind  接下来是腹语术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么都是即兴表演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  你的金发真美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  绫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝的头发尝起来就像蜂蜜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我表演得这么变态  而且你明明有在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是没天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不能一蹴而就的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  再来转一次盘子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连阳子都这么消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比较喜欢阳光向上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绫的腹语术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我昨天弄坏了美月的玩具熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修得好随便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…姐姐你居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.25,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实我不该用有色胶布  我应该用透明胶布的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会这么粗鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的  我补好熊夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  去和美月和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一下子就修好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  忍你太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦  忍可厉害了  忍是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是天赋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后忍可以成为专业服装设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  忍  你可以做设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设计师？好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  以后你就是世界闻名的大宫设计师了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我想做的是翻译…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都是有适合做的和不适合做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝也是会心一击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是忍你还是要努力的话  我会为你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是还不行的话  就由我来做翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有什么意义…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要为你加油了  没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始学习  查50个英语单词每个抄50遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  太严厉了  抄10次行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要严格要求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严格要求  严格要求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不让她本人认真起来  也是学不到什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在马鼻子前挂个萝卜它就会跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对忍来说就是金发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么挂个金发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她充满了干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是最好的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算忍不擅长英语  但至少她很喜欢外国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我特别喜欢爱丽丝和可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子你喜欢吃饭所以是个贪吃鬼对吧  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是食欲而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预习复习和作业我全都自己做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是正常水平而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己聪明了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这是下一本习题集  再接再厉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脑过度  晕乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍你看上去一直都是晕乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的路上要不要去哪里走走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  走  我想吃可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错  挺有年轻人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要巧克力蛋羹味的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要栗子巧克力味的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃带草莓的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  我就要苹果肉桂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好吃的嘛  给我吃一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也给你吃吃  约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳真是耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  今天没有体育课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一路赛跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春真是个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在学生时代的时候一直专心学习
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没享受过青春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久世桥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有心享受  什么年纪都能享受青春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌丸老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违地来个举手击掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举手击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.71,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,举手击掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌丸老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图腾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵  喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要发给穗乃花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月  忍帮我补好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  补得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么姐姐会那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍她一定能成为一个翻译的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是她的老相识  不会看错的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂你的意思  但感觉就像个监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  毕竟忍就像妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你先担心一下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}自己的成绩烂得没资格说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月  你还在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道阳子有没有和美月和好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是发不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇  忍她们快回来了  来帮我做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航空邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱丽丝的妈妈寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是英国的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  你回信的时候可以让我也写几句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想用英语写信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要翻辞典写  所以大概会花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也是成为翻译的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  先用罗马音写出原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你直接写下日语然后翻译成英语比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一封国际邮件还是用罗马字写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
